name: Dynafit Low Tech Race 105 Bindings Manual - Unisex
description: Exceptionally light bindings for ultra-fast ski mountaineering or ski running missions. Forged aluminum and high-strength synthetics weigh in at 105g. They are solid on the descents and nimble on the ascents. They're the ultimate skimo race bindings.Made of 7075 aluminum and high-strength plastic for an exceptionally lightness.Stainless steel plate adds extra sturdiness to the heel mechanism.Icebreaker toe pins snap in ultra-fast and resist ice buildup.Torx screws provide outstanding stability.Optimized hole patterns for screws.Manual lock version.
